{
  "stem": "5970.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then after a while, I suppose I had a lucky break then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We are standing on the Pilplatz, on this big square being counted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this SS woman that was in charge, this Elsa Erich, chose me to be their maid.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She asked me to come out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she looked me over like I was a piece of merchandise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she said I must report now and work as a maid for the SS women.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But before that happened, I lost my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My mother was sent to another camp from Plaszow a few weeks after we arrived there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My father was killed by the guards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was just beaten to death a few weeks after we arrived there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my little sister was still there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But she was kept in a separate block with all the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I couldn't see her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I could see her perhaps once a week on a Sunday, when we didn't work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Then I could go and see here there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But otherwise, they were isolated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "All the children were in a special block.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were not nice people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they chose-- you know, whoever would do a job like that wasn't a nice person because I had a cousin in the ghetto, a young man, who was chosen to be a policeman in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he did go because, you know, it was something to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as I said, once you had a job, you-- you were safe for the time being.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You weren't sent away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he worked as a policeman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was a very, very nice, kind young man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first time they asked him to go and arrest Jews, he said, don't be silly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not going to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
